sentiment_score_definition: x <= -0.35: Bearish; -0.35 < x <= -0.15: Somewhat-Bearish; -0.15 < x < 0.15: Neutral; 0.15 <= x < 0.35: Somewhat_Bullish; x >= 0.35: Bullish
relevance_score_definition: 0 < x <= 1, with a higher score indicating higher relevance.

feed.title: Certain Class B Ordinary Shares of Cal Redwood Acquisition Corp. are subject to a Lock-Up Agreement Ending on 19-NOV-2025.
feed.summary: Certain Class B Ordinary Shares of Cal Redwood Acquisition Corp. are subject to a lock-up agreement that ends on November 19, 2025. This lock-up period, lasting 181 days from May 22, 2025, restricts the company's directors and officers from offering, selling, or otherwise disposing of these shares without prior written consent.
